Possible "inventory" field values:
	- PrimaryWeapon
	- SecondaryWeapon
	- Armor
	- UtilityPouch
	- SupportGear (use SupportGear1/2/3 for exclusive items, like for camera/hammer/lockpickmachine)

Possible "Class" field values:
	- Pointman
	- Assault
	- Breacher
	- Stealth
	- Shield
	- PointmanEnemy
